sentences: She was born in Portland, Oregon of Chinese-Korean parents.
She has also recorded with Soulwax, and appears in the film Part of the Weekend Never Dies.
Among other artists, she was featured on Shit Robot's first album From the Cradle to the Rave in 2010 and on his third 2016 album What follows on the track Lose Control.
Nancy was also featured in Classixx's All You're Waiting For from their album Hanging Gardens in 2013.
